msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Attendances`: מבוסס על :doc:`approved checked-in hours <../../"
"attendances/management>` באפליקציית **Attendances**."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:148
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:143
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:130
